    <item>
      <title>乌克兰放松了一些战时企业资本管制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/ukraine-eases-some-wartime-capital-controls-for-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰央行放宽了部分企业外汇限制，此举被称为自 2022 年俄罗斯全面入侵以来最大规模的货币市场自由化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/ukraine-eases-some-wartime-capital-controls-for-businesses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 19:45:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部将于 5 月 28 日决定波音是否违反起诉协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/doj-to-decide-if-boeing-breached-prosecution-deal-by-may-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据发送给受害者家属律师的一封电子邮件，美国司法部计划在 5 月 28 日之前决定波音公司是否违反了该公司为逃避与两架 737 Max 飞机坠毁相关的刑事指控而达成的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/doj-to-decide-if-boeing-breached-prosecution-deal-by-may-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 19:05:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七国集团关注美国主导的 500 亿美元乌克兰援助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/g-7-eyes-plan-on-us-led-50-billion-aid-package-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正与其亲密伙伴进行谈判，牵头一个盟友团体向乌克兰提供高达 500 亿美元的援助，这笔巨额支出将用被冻结的俄罗斯主权资产的暴利来偿还 — — 这些资产正在产生利息 — — 主要是在欧洲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/g-7-eyes-plan-on-us-led-50-billion-aid-package-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:48:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度国民被指控在加拿大谋杀锡克教活动人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/arrests-made-in-sikh-activist-s-murder-in-canada-reports-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大警方周五以一级谋杀罪指控三名印度公民杀害了一名著名的锡克教活动人士，并表示官员正在积极调查与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府的联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/arrests-made-in-sikh-activist-s-murder-in-canada-reports-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党走向权力之路：英国选举的五个要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/uk-local-elections-labour-on-course-for-power-and-other-takeaways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政的保守党在周四的一系列地方选举中遭遇惨败，这让人们更加感觉总理苏纳克在九个月内必须举行​​的大选之前将难以扭转局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/uk-local-elections-labour-on-course-for-power-and-other-takeaways</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西希望淡水河谷下一任首席执行官与政府更加接近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/brazil-wants-vale-s-next-ceo-to-have-closer-ties-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西预计，全球第二大铁矿石生产商淡水河谷公司的下一任首席执行官将与官员和监管机构建立更密切的关系，尽管公众对政府对公司继任计划的影响力的审查扰乱了今年早些时候的领导层搜寻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/brazil-wants-vale-s-next-ceo-to-have-closer-ties-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院民主党人奎利亚尔被指控收受外国贿赂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/justice-department-expected-to-indict-house-democrat-cuellar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州众议院民主党人亨利·奎利亚尔 (Henry Cuellar) 及其妻子因涉嫌收受约 60 万美元的外国贿赂而被起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/justice-department-expected-to-indict-house-democrat-cuellar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 15:45:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马法院批准总统领跑者的候选资格，引发债券反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/panama-court-decision-on-frontrunner-sparks-bond-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马最高法院为领跑者何塞·劳尔·穆利诺(Jose Raul Mulino)参加周日的总统选举扫清了道路，消除了市场的一个关键风险，该国债券上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/panama-court-decision-on-frontrunner-sparks-bond-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:44:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将奥巴马医改范围扩大到缺乏健康计划的“梦想家”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/daca-recipients-to-get-obamacare-access-through-biden-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统将允许一群无证美国居民根据《平价医疗法案》获得医疗保险，这一变化是在总统竞选团队希望打入拉丁裔社区之际做出的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/daca-recipients-to-get-obamacare-access-through-biden-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
